{"tid":1440191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望可以有唔同語言的文宣（傳單）","createTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T11:22:57.000Z","uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"872a8347f05770f360e84273a74472b246ef1354","tid":1440191,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"去到而家直路 向唔同國家ge 人宣傳香港發生緊ge 事變得更重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以希望文宣部可以將一張poster 翻譯到唔同語言例如英文 (簡體中文大家可以再商議下 雖然我好反對用簡體字但係為左等蝗都知香港發生咩事，少少讓步都要做下）等機場做和理非ge 手足可以派單張針軔外國人 同外國人解釋下香港發生緊咩事  又可以係多旅客ge lennon wall 到貼 等d 旅客可以閱讀一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"f546014ca7899fd90d5d40ee7437e87d9d2171cb","tid":1440191,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04e56a5850b92bfb721f4ec8317e81390894933f","tid":1440191,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5169c064d431f23e8f7e0cc0d4b8999e9ff72b4","tid":1440191,"uid":13382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f240547cca1d007d267a6ae712d7ac58adc6841","tid":1440191,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2c3c58e6b43a5a7c85236402419430d8803168","tid":1440191,"uid":277993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081c9c722089e627a9f4c25d5b792bb61c17ad8e","tid":1440191,"